		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Armor (Any Light, Medium, or Heavy) - Very Rare (Requires Attunement)</p><p><em>Spiked plates forged in the Abyss sharpen your strikes and whisper infernal secrets.</em></p><p><strong>Properties</strong></p><ul><li><p>While wearing the armor, you gain a +1 bonus to &amp;Reference[Armor Class] and you understand &amp;Reference[Abyssal].</p></li><li><p>The clawed gauntlets cause your Unarmed Strikes to deal [[/damage 1d8 slashing]] damage instead of bludgeoning, and you gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls for those strikes.</p></li></ul><section><p><strong>Curse.</strong> Once donned, the armor cannot be removed except by <em>Remove Curse</em> or similar magic. While wearing it, you have &amp;Reference[Disadvantage] on &amp;Reference[attack rolls] against demons and on &amp;Reference[saving throws] against their spells and special abilities.</p></section><p>@Embed[Compendium.dnd5e.content24.JournalEntry.dmgFoundryRefere.JournalEntryPage.Ok4iCgD25ENgoRxE cite=false caption=false classes=\"hide-in-embed\"]</p>",
